_sText:
At this map I wanted that CTs and Ts fight with cars. A round stars at street where there are about 16 cars and 2 bus for every team

Terrorists have to plant a bomb at the middle of the map so you have to very fast and play cooperative becoause Cts will try that the bomb does not explode!
Maybe the map can be medium if you drive a car.

Counterrorist have to defend the streets.

The round time is about 4:10. There are:

-Buy zone at the middle of the map / near of your base.

-Areas where you can be cured.

-Weapons at your own base.

If this map is successfull, I will make other one with nice textures!

There is a radar so you will not get lost ^^ HF
